text.tspan: Brush: head types, compostions, and brush size
Head types are according to hairs size/length,
method of composition. Size and length allow
large or small writings, types and composition
make flexibility or rigidity and rebound.

text.tspan: Type 2 : Zhu/Bei, rigid hairs inside, soft hairs
Type 3 : Jiānháo, mix in heart and ring, very
soft in skin. a : Anatomy with heart, ring, skin.
The height of the brush hold influence
control and velocity. The calligrapher choice
his brush mainly according to which styles he
want to write down, and with which size.
